        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278376289">
            DAY2槟榔谷，呀诺达走起！槟榔谷文化底蕴很好！能看到黎族的生活环境！呀诺达热带雨林也不错哦！很适合拍照！
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278378594" data-seq="278378595" data-pid="278378594" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
