            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278379300">
            DAY3天涯海角真的很美！座快艇感觉超级爽，走时候可以在门口买点小水果香皂作为礼物送给朋友们！
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278379514" data-seq="278379515" data-pid="278379514" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8163382/278379514.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:680px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/AC/E5/wKgBEFpJ1-6Adz0zAAR8D0r7_Ak43.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/AC/E5/wKgBEFpJ1-6Adz0zAAR8D0r7_Ak43.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278379514" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278380252">
            DAY4我返回了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>当地有一个万人海鲜市场，真的比<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>划算太多了，四百块，大龙虾大螃蟹简直吃到嗨，如果去<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>的朋友我推荐一定要去那里！<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>的市场海鲜和加工价格都是统一物价局定价的！肯定不会宰人，而且环境又干净！服务也不错！
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278380511" data-seq="278380512" data-pid="278380511" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:640px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8163382/278380511.html">
